BasicNavigableKeyValueIndex
public interface NavigableKeyValueIndex<K extends IndexKeyEntry<K>,V extends IndexEntry>
extends java.util.NavigableMap<K,V>, KeyValueIndex<K,V>

Interface to any navigable key value index structure. Defines a navigable map with ability to initialize from a file, and to dump it's content to a file.
